Class ClassPathScanner.ApkClassFinder

  • java.lang.Object
    • vogar.target.ClassPathScanner.ApkClassFinder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ClassPathScanner.ClassFinder
    Enclosing class:
    ClassPathScanner

    static class ClassPathScanner.ApkClassFinder
extends java.lang.Object
implements ClassPathScanner.ClassFinder
    Finds all classes and sub packages that are below the packageName and add them to the respective sets. Searches the package in a single APK.

    This class uses the Android-only class DexFile. This class will fail to load on non-Android VMs.
